{"tid":1091121,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"律政司終極敗訴 終院廢不誠實取用電腦「萬能key」武功","createTime":"2019-04-04T02:24:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-04T09:03:24.000Z","uid":23734,"like":25,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"a58557b418a23baa1cd849365d6fd942c408a796","tid":1091121,"uid":23734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:24:03.000Z","msg":"//終院非常任法官范禮全在判詞中提到，「取用」指未獲授權下使用電腦，該詞與使用自己的設備的情況格格不相入，法例原意界定電腦罪行時，提述的都是使用或誤用不屬於犯罪者本人的電腦，這觀點被其他終院法官採納並同意。//<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190404/59447828\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59447828&d=xTo9lt5%2FMO3GrXFnFHQdvAjMvzJQG4GdM8cyRMJzdLg%3D&h=fd111b48\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190404%2F59447828&h=bea13d69\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20190404/59447828</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b302392f5b9daf766054a6ce73f4d75d34403d2","tid":1091121,"uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:24:36.000Z","msg":"檢控萬能Key<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ae3ec504bb3a2b64ff4e21746adccb53b4aa944","tid":1091121,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35ec417d1466e3f9d93c96dc26b8d930a2b11cb6","tid":1091121,"uid":23734,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-04T02:52:40.000Z","msg":"之後偷拍港女裙底，律政司係咪淨係可以用 #metoo提告<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji